Key Match Events: Mitchell Marsh scored an unbeaten 177 off 132 balls.
Australia won by 8 wickets with 32 balls remaining.
Towhid Hridoy scored 74 off 79 balls for Bangladesh.
Adam Zampa took 2 wickets for 32 runs.
Sean Abbott took 2 wickets for 61 runs.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Mitchell Marsh was named Player of the Match.
Australia elected to field first after winning the toss.
The match was held at Maharashtra Cricket Association Stadium, Pune.
